<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>We have recently made numerous attempts to contact you</b></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> in relation to your query.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Unfortunately, we have not been successful in getting in touch, so </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">we have closed this matter internally</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you do still wish to discuss this with us, please feel free to give us a call on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
